## Test Coverage

### QueryTimeoutError Class
- Creates error with correct properties (timeoutSeconds, query)
- getUserMessage() returns user-friendly message
- getHint() returns optimization suggestions

### isTimeoutError Function
- Returns true for QueryTimeoutError
- Returns true for AbortError
- Returns true for errors with "timeout" message
