### formatTimeoutError Function
- Returns formatted object with message, userMessage, hint, code
- Uses ClickHouse error code 159 (TIMEOUT_EXCEEDED)

### Error Handling Verification
- QueryTimeoutError provides clear, actionable error messages
- Error includes timeout duration and optimization hints
